Thursday, April 18, 1991

DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

89-1397. In re Resignation of Moore.

Upon consideration of movant William Julius Moore’s Motion for Interpretation of the September 13, 1989 Order of this court accepting William Julius Moore’s resignation as an attorney and counselor at law, IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion be, and hereby is, granted, effective April 17, 1991.
